---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <Nav />
  
  <main class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="mini-header">
        <nav class="breadcrumbs">
          <a href="/" class="bc-link">EASY ECOM</a>
          <span class="bc-sep">/</span>
          <a href="/about" class="bc-link active">ABOUT</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="profile-hero">
        <div class="profile-image-container">
          <img src="/images/alex.png" alt="Alex R" class="profile-image" />
        </div>
        <div class="profile-info">
          <h1 class="alex-name">ALEX R</h1>
          <p class="alex-title">Ecommerce Specialist & Analyst</p>
          <div class="mission-statement">
            <h2 class="mission-tag">THE MISSION:</h2>
            <p class="mission-text">NO GUESSING. JUST DATA.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-content">
        <div class="content-grid">
          <div class="content-block">
            <h3>THE PROBLEM</h3>
            <p>
              The ecommerce ecosystem is a gold rush, but most founders are being sold "shovels" that don't actually dig. You’ve seen the paid affiliate lists - they tell you a plugin is "essential" because they get a commission, not because the code is efficient.
            </p>
            <p>
              Every time you install an unvetted app on Shopify or a bloated plugin on WooCommerce, you aren't just adding a feature; you're adding a liability.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block">
            <h3>THE SOLUTION: EASY ECOM</h3>
            <p>
              I created Easy Ecom to be the technical filter the industry lacks. I don’t do "top 10" lists based on vibes. I do audits. 
            </p>
            <p>
              I test, break, and fix Shopify and WooCommerce stores so you don’t have to. When I review an app or a protocol, I’m looking at the raw math behind your margins and the stability of your checkout.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block">
            <h3>WHO IS BEHIND THIS?</h3>
            <p>
              My background is in the technical trenches - testing, breaking, and fixing the architecture that powers high-volume stores. 
            </p>
            <p>
              This site is my public ledger of those tests. It’s high-density research, editorial deep-dives, and technical protocols designed for the founder who cares more about their conversion rate than the hype.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block">
            <h3>OUR CORE PROTOCOLS</h3>
            <ul class="protocol-list">
              <li>
                <strong>Zero Affiliation:</strong> If a tool is featured here, it’s because it survived the test, not because someone paid for the slot.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Technical Transparency:</strong> We show the "why" behind the verdict - whether it’s a database query bottleneck or a bloated JavaScript execution.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Founder Focused:</strong> Content is written for the people who actually have to live with the technical decisions they make.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-section">
          <p>Tired of guessing which plugin works? <a href="#" class="ledger-link">Join the Ledger</a> and let's look at the data.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding-top: 8rem;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-bottom: 8rem;
  }

  .mini-header {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--zinc-200);
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .breadcrumbs {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  }

  .bc-link {
    color: var(--zinc-500);
    transition: var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .bc-link:hover {
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .bc-link.active {
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .bc-sep {
    color: var(--zinc-300);
  }

  .profile-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 400px 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .profile-image-container {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid var(--black);
    box-shadow: 20px 20px 0px var(--primary);
  }

  .profile-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    filter: grayscale(100%);
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .profile-image-container:hover .profile-image {
    filter: grayscale(0%);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .alex-name {
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem);
    line-height: 0.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .alex-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .mission-statement {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border-left: 8px solid var(--black);
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .mission-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--zinc-500);
  }

  .mission-text {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    max-width: 600px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about-content {
    border-top: 2px solid var(--black);
    padding-top: 5rem;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem 6rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .content-block h3 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    background: var(--primary);
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
  }

  .content-block p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--zinc-900);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .protocol-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .protocol-list li {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--zinc-800);
  }

  .protocol-list strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .ledger-link {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 8px;
    text-decoration-thickness: 3px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .profile-hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; text-align: center; }
    .profile-image-container { max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .mission-statement { margin: 0 auto; border-left: none; border-top: 8px solid var(--black); padding-left: 0; padding-top: 2rem; }
    .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4rem; }
    .mission-text { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .alex-name { font-size: 3.5rem; }
    .cta-section { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.25rem; }
  }
</style>
